data.description: **MOTIVATED SELLERS** Wonderfully private mountain retreat nestled among mature woods with mountain views! New roof, new paint, new deck, new light fixtures and hardware. This beautiful home offers an abundance of space for entertaining inside and out and a plethora of storage! All 4 bedrooms upstairs have walk-in closets. Enjoy the long-range view and low-maintenance landscaping from the spacious new deck. 2+ acres and a trail to the creek offer plenty of room to explore the beauty of WNC nature ~ sit on boulders while you enjoy the creek and then cozy up inside by the woodburning stove! Large rec room opens out back to the oversized, new hot tub! Multizoned: Each floor has its own heat pump. High-speed internet! Short-term rentals allowed! Buried utility lines for unobstructed views. The mortgage may be assumable at the 2.625% interest rate! Buyer to verify with Freedom Mortgage.
